modName: Female Press Out The Wrinkles and Forehead v3
summary: Replaces the face wrinkles of human and elven races, only female.
descriptionHtml:
Female Press Out The Wrinkles v3.0 - By.WindSong




>> Description

v2.0 

I\'m really tired out of waiting. So I made this mode myself.
This mod replaces the face wrinkles of human and elven races, only Female .
But not Orcs. Because I think about wrinkles of a orc is a chaming point:)

This mod was made on Xenius\'s mod. Thank you.
This mod isn\'t required any other modes. 

v3.0

- I tried hard to decreased Blocky phenomenon.
It was impossible. But finally i find out the reason.
DTX(method of save) is lossy compression method.
So I exchanged my DDS file\'s save method DTX into 8.8.8.8.
8.8.8.8 has supported high resolution normalmap.
This version has decreased Blocky phenomenon.

- I mended skin more naturally. 
Never mind if you can\'t notice that:\'(

- I exchanged Xenius\'s \'Detailed Faces v1.0\' into \'Detailed Faces v1.3\'
It\'s awesome! :) I love you Xenius! But I\'m not a girl.


I\'m sorry that I can\'t English well. So, it\'s done.




>> Installation

I recommend using 7zip to extract the files.
Move the Data folder to your Skyrim folder.




>> Uninstallation

Remove the following files:

Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\bretonfemale\\femalehead_msn.dds
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\darkelffemale\\femalehead_msn.dds
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\female\\femalehead_msn.dds
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\female\\astridhead_msn
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\femaleold\\femalehead_msn.dds
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\femaleorc\\femalehead_msn.dds
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\highelffemale\\femalehead_msn.dds
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\imperialfemale\\femalehead_msn.dds
Data\\textures\\actors\\character\\redguardfemale\\femalehead_msn.dds
same files etc.



>> Requirements

- Skyrim.

>> Credits

Special Thanks to the following people

Xenius   - for the readme :)
Xenius   - for the skin resource - Detailed Faces v1.3 :)
Bethesda - for creating Skyrim




>> Distribution Permission

- You may use the content for your own mods, permission is not needed, just notify me.
- You may not redistribute this mod in any way or claim it as your own.




>> P.S.

But I only play to middle age male:)
This mod wasn\'t made for me. It\'s yours.


--------------------------------------------------------------------------------End
